reviewText: I love this tape. It was the funniest I've ever seen! But, I wish they could sell Nanna and Lil' Puss Puss the Nanthology for $5.00.

I'm very sorry this great group of cartoons have not been converted to DVD. I will have to find myself a VCR just so I can continue to watch this, Skippy the dog food tester and Off on a Comet. DNA get with it! Give up your day jobs and slyly slip out again! Your fan club calls.

This is by far the most hilarious cartoon I have ever seen in my entire life! I laughed so hard I had tears streaming down my face and well lets just say....next time I watch it I will definately be wearing "Depends" I highly recommend this video! If you like the Simpsons......you will absolutely love "Nanna and Lil' Puss Puss"
The only thing more fun than watching this video was making this video. I whole-heartedly recommend it. Buy a bunch of 'em!
